title: Pro Bowl vs. Eazy-E vs. Magic
itunes:title: Pro Bowl vs. Eazy-E vs. Magic
description: Anthony and Gregg are back to talk about the hot mic situation going on in the NFL and how Anthony deserves a fly over. They reflect on times when they've had issues with each other in the past and Gregg actually has some notes. It's a depressing week, the pro bowl is cancelled, a man goes to jail for farting, a priest has sex on the altar, and a senator stuffs cash up his butt cheeks.
